data.description: Welcome Home!! This 4 bd 2bth Kendall home built in 2017 is in pristine condition and is ready for its new owner. You're immediately greeted by an over-sized driveway and beautiful well-kept landscaping as you enter this tastefully designed floorplan. This home offers an ample amount of storage space, granite countertops in both the kitchen and bathrooms, ceramic tile throughout with carpet in the spacious bedrooms, and so much more! Step outside to your large fenced in backyard which has flatwork added for a back patio and a storage shed equipped with lighting and electricity. Another plus is this home is set up with reverse feed if power goes out, all you have to do is plug in a generator! Take advantage of this rare opportunity to get tucked away in this friendly community while not having any front or back neighbors! This gem will not last long so schedule your private showing today!!
